data.description: This stunning 3 bed, 2 bath home with a Den Boast over 1770 sq ft is perfect for those seeking both comfort and style. Inside you'll be greeted by an open floor plan, with vaulted ceilings and newly laid luxury tile floors that have. Freshened up with new paint inside and out and upgraded light fixtures and fans. The roof was replaced in 2019. The dining room is perfect for hosting dinner parties, with plenty of room for all your loved ones. The split floor plan is perfect for those seeking privacy. The master bathroom features a tub and separate tile shower, making it the perfect space to relax and unwind. The Jack & Jill bathroom goes into the 2 guest beds and den. Large yard and has City water and City sewer. Close to SWFL International airport, shopping and restaurants, Jet Blue Boston Red Sox baseball stadium, and the Minnesota Twins stadium! New Roof! New Tile Floors!
